{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make child abandonment by a parent a criminal offence ",
        "additional_details": "Abandonment is classed as neglect, but we believe absent parents face no accountability and scrutiny falls on the parent who stays. Making child abandonment by a parent a criminal offence could ensure the system is fairer and both parents are held equally responsible.",
        "background": "We call on the Government to update child protection and family law by making child abandonment by a parent a criminal offence.",
